


   ##        ltalk          ##
This project is example about talk server,
basic with tcp protocol,but server use line
as basic message mode,like '****\r\n',
so client use telnet command at terminal will 
supported well.

step 1
    telnet ip port

step 2
    enter -help to get more command infomation

step 3 
    registe usename

step 4 
    login server

step 5 
    talk to group or one gay who your known her or his id


note: this only an exercise with Erlang






